commit.message:
Remove Rresult dependency for the bos library.

It remains for `bos.setup` though.
Bow to OCaml's new default warnings.
Fix Os.Dir.create on existing files to error instead of being non-sensical.

Fix bug in OS.Dir.create

The function returned [false] instead of [true] when
a directory was created with `path:false`.
OS.File.read: use Unix.lseek to decide if the file is a stream.

Built-in support for tool search.

Tweak `OS.Cmd.{exist,must_exist}`. Add
`OS.Cmd.{find_tool,get_tool,resolve,search_path_dirs}`.

Closes #53.
Deprecate Cmd.[get_]line_exec in favor of Cmd.[get_]line_tool.

Fix OS.Path.symlink ~force:true when the forced file is a symlink.

Closes #75.
